# Unity Puzzle Game - Supply Chain Project

A Unity-based puzzle game featuring multiple gameplay mechanics and VR compatibility. This project demonstrates advanced game development techniques including puzzle design, game state management, and virtual reality integration.

## üéÆ Game Overview

This puzzle game combines various interactive elements and challenges designed to engage players through problem-solving mechanics. The project includes both traditional desktop gameplay and an experimental VR implementation.

### Core Features
- **Multiple Puzzle Types**: Various interactive puzzle mechanics
- **Game State Management**: Comprehensive game flow control
- **VR Support**: Experimental virtual reality implementation
- **Modular Architecture**: Clean separation of gameplay systems

## üõ†Ô∏è Technical Stack

- **Engine**: Unity (Latest LTS)
- **Platform**: PC (Windows/Mac/Linux)
- **VR Support**: Oculus/Meta Quest compatible (experimental)
- **Programming Language**: C#
- **Input Systems**: Traditional controls + VR controllers

## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

### Core Systems

#### Game Management
- **GameManager**: Central control system for game flow and state management
- **Puzzle System**: Modular puzzle framework supporting multiple puzzle types
- **State Management**: Robust game state tracking and transitions
- **Scene Management**: Seamless transitions between game areas

#### Puzzle Mechanics
- **Interactive Elements**: Physics-based puzzle interactions
- **Logic Systems**: Complex puzzle validation and progression
- **User Interface**: Intuitive puzzle interaction feedback
- **Progress Tracking**: Save system for puzzle completion status

#### VR Implementation
- **VR Compatibility**: Experimental virtual reality support
- **Hand Tracking**: VR controller integration for puzzle interaction
- **Immersive UI**: 3D user interface elements for VR environments
- **Comfort Features**: VR-specific user experience optimizations

